{"tid":1115480,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有時教補習真的好灰","createTime":"2019-04-19T08:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T09:24:43.000Z","uid":249342,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9901a42a9de703810a754fddb209af76d1a8d6e7","tid":1115480,"uid":249342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"自問自己學歷都唔錯, Master畢業, 高教經濟A<br />\n自己對自己既教學方法都好有信心<br />\n打個比如: 經濟科最重要既其實係邏輯基礎,要打好個底<br />\n<br />\n但有時候教學生真係教到灰, 有時佢地誤信啲補習天王, 以為有多skill就等於有用."},{"pid":"155e7741c23d84ae68a6a947daaa4b3af6484fc6","tid":1115480,"uid":36383,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:46:54.000Z","msg":"<del>經濟</del>所有科最重要既其實係邏輯基礎,要打好個底"},{"pid":"8af20787092d9adf19e747d10f441193923b4928","tid":1115480,"uid":71237,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"將邏輯基礎變做一種skills嚟包裝囉<br />\n<br />\n有時啲學生唔係唔相信你果套，只係佢地唔知道點樣先可以跟你諗得一樣咁有邏輯。<br />\n<br />\n就咁叫佢地&quot;step by step諗得有邏輯啲&quot;係唔夠。"},{"pid":"e2fb49b741adf6b6161815ec800e54a99f4bd72f","tid":1115480,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:27:46.000Z","msg":"Can i ask you something about how to find NE in calculus (Game theory) ????<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95ff6de6d6ee1a08569233d7b825d8fd83300c4","tid":1115480,"uid":54270,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:35:34.000Z","msg":"佢地好多skill都係日校唔會教但大學教而且係考試用useful<br />\n另一種係靠pastpaper個ans屈返個skill出來<br />\n<br />\n但可悲中學生為求高分，寧信假流野都唔信其他人"},{"pid":"0eba8fbafba37476b4add79c7f9b8dbf1bf349b8","tid":1115480,"uid":76419,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:37:14.000Z","msg":"跟過cliff yeung就知econ無skill既喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋樓主講得岩 econ一定講concept"},{"pid":"108c9537986127f773a41ca2a8ae781633b84fd7","tid":1115480,"uid":72825,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"簡單一句，你教得唔好"},{"pid":"3d37f87a59e0dd0d6abd623c276190496ac7482b","tid":1115480,"uid":1788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"有人將elasticity 同Total revenue 既關係用skill 包裝，然後d學生覺得答MC 好有用，因為唔洗plug d數字入elasticity 個條式<br />\n<br />\n樓主可以參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7775d0616705cb7f6f79bbcdbe6033c1c71a478","tid":1115480,"uid":1788,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e95ff6de6d6ee1a08569233d7b825d8fd83300c4","tid":1115480,"uid":54270,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:35:34.000Z","msg":"佢地好多skill都係日校唔會教但大學教而且係考試用useful<br />\n另一種係靠pastpaper個ans屈返個skill出來<br />\n<br />\n但可悲中學生為求高分，寧信假流野都唔信其他人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:40:20.000Z","msg":"DSE econ 無乜大學野岩用既，數學就有好多<br />\n<br />\n下面個個就有d用既，我知有好多人會覺得搞咁多無聊野做乜，econ世界concept &gt;&gt; all，尤其dse 根本只係唔同包裝問一樣內容，呢幾點我絕對同意。<br />\n<br />\n但唔好忽略有一班同學佢地邏輯差，抽象思維能力弱，我地都要教佢地。將一d抽象概念用現實既「答題技巧」包裝係2nd best option。<br />\n<br />\n尤其對一d諗野無方向既同學。佢地望到題目就覺得係火星文，做唔到link翻concept呢一步。<br />\n<br />\n要比d hint佢地，同佢地講題目問x既，就用一個x 既framework去諗。<br />\n<br />\n同埋 &lsquo;skill&rsquo; 比 &lsquo;concept&rsquo; 吸引係呢個世代中學生既普遍思維。"},{"pid":"a7803f778cf775230a0e2a8a5eb4f84a301742c6","tid":1115480,"uid":62332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:40:31.000Z","msg":"學歷高就等於教得好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2ccb363ef89335963d773d7c1a4c83389afd56","tid":1115480,"uid":160884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"試下將concepts生活化"}]}